+## Overview
+
+Total revenue across all orders was $7,154.44 from 30 orders, with a median order value of $204.95.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget generated the most revenue at $2,392.00, despite selling only 16 units across 7 orders, reflecting its premium $149.50 price. Widget followed at $2,118.94 from 106 units and 10 orders, the highest order count of any product. Doohickey earned $1,513.00, and Sprocket earned $1,130.50, the latter driven by high volume (238 units) at a low $4.75 price.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North led all regions with $2,176.35 in revenue across 8 orders, followed by East at $1,830.79. South generated $1,732.48, also from 8 orders, while West trailed at $1,414.82 despite matching East's 7 orders.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Promote Gadget bundles or upsells, since its high price point drives outsized revenue despite low unit volume.
+- Investigate West's lower revenue versus East despite similar order counts; consider targeted regional promotions.
+- Continue driving Sprocket volume, since its low price still yields solid returns when sold in bulk.
